s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/b0rd1\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">b0rd1<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 27, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">simple and nice plugin, great job!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">good job<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/muhammetdkaya\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dbed9cc9107ea97baa43b4d59cf7138b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dbed9cc9107ea97baa43b4d59cf7138b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/muhammetdkaya\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">muhammetdkaya<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 23, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I like this plugin<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does the job<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dantianhealth\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/820b9a440237540803a95f6b4e18450c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/820b9a440237540803a95f6b4e18450c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dantianhealth\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jason Chong <small>(DantianHealth)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 23, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It's is simple but effective.\nI'd love to see this have a few more options eg set a break point for it show or not (ie keep it to mobile only), increase padding top\/bottom and also have less than 5 tabs as a choice.\nBut great plugin plugging a big hole in what has been available so far\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and great plugin, saved me dozen hours<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/echowosh2019\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/48c5102533695a908ada9bc7194a62c5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/48c5102533695a908ada9bc7194a62c5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/echowosh2019\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">echowosh2019<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 22, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Hi there,\n\nWe been using this ages old hamburger nav bar for a while and I just hated it. I was planning to use some jquery\/css solutions to create a homemade tabbar for ourselves, and then I found this plugin. \n\nTo be honest, it is still buggy and not flexible enough, but it just saved my life for hours development.\n\nGreat job, trying to donate so the author can keep working on this, but the donation link somehow not working. Would be great if the author can provide some other way for donation.\n\nsuggestions for future development\n1. better icon support, ionic, etc. The current wp default icons just not look cool enough\n2. configable icon size\n3. There are chances ppl have 5 tabs, yet the center one is just a giant icon without text, would be good to support that. Now I have to create a js to specially reset the center icon size\n4. Looks like for the icon, your code simply add a prefix onto it, could be wrong if ppl get the icon code directly from dashicon page\n5. A nice animation effect will be great\n\nAnyway, really appreciate for this plugin, simple yet helpful. thx<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Add fixed bottom menu.",
    "description": "<p>Add fixed bottom menu.<\/p>\n<h4>Links<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Five link destinations can be specified.<\/li>\n<li>Provides filters for icons, URLs, and text for each link.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Options<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Can specify the number of columns from 3 to 5.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the font size.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the menu height.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the line height.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the padding top.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the color of text, buttons, and mouse over.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the upper limit of the display width.<\/li>\n<li>Can specify the stack order of css elemental.<\/li>\n<li>The above options filters are provided.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Other filters<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide a filter to erase the menu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Demo<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/fbm.riverforest-wp.info\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Fixed Bottom Menu Live<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Icons<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/developer.wordpress.org\/resource\/dashicons\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Dashicons<\/a> can be specified.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Customize<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Template files allow for flexible <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/katsushi-kawamori\/Fixed-Bottom-Menu-Templates\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">customization<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>The default template file is template\/fixedbottommenu-template-html.php and template\/fixedbottommenu-template-css.php. Using this as a reference, you can specify a separate template file using the filters below.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<pre><code>\/** ==================================================\n * Filter for template file of html.\n *\n *\/\nadd_filter(\n    'fixed_bottom_menu_generate_template_html_file',\n    function () {\n        $wp_uploads = wp_upload_dir();\n        $upload_dir = wp_normalize_path( $wp_uploads['basedir'] );\n        $upload_dir = untrailingslashit( $upload_dir );\n        return $upload_dir . '\/tmp\/fixedbottommenu-template-html.php';\n    },\n    10,\n    1\n);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<pre><code>\/** ==================================================\n * Filter for template file of css.\n *\n *\/\nadd_filter(\n    'fixed_bottom_menu_generate_template_css_file',\n    function () {\n        $wp_uploads = wp_upload_dir();\n        $upload_dir = wp_normalize_path( $wp_uploads['basedir'] );\n        $upload_dir = untrailingslashit( $upload_dir );\n        return $upload_dir . '\/tmp\/fixedbottommenu-template-css.php';\n    },\n    10,\n    1\n);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<ul>\n<li>CSS files can be set separately. Please see the filters below.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<pre><code>\/** ==================================================\n * Filter for CSS file.\n *\n *\/\nadd_filter(\n    'fixed_bottom_menu_css_url',\n    function () {\n        $wp_uploads = wp_upload_dir();\n        $upload_url = $wp_uploads['baseurl'];\n        if ( is_ssl() ) {\n            $upload_url = str_replace( 'http:', 'https:', $upload_url );\n        }\n        $upload_url = untrailingslashit( $upload_url );\n        return $upload_url . '\/tmp\/fixedbottommenu.css';\n    },\n    10,\n    1\n);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
